ered about photons. Confirmed Bohr's complementarity principle — any path information gathered causes the interference pattern to vanish. Directly disproved Einstein's 1927 hypothesis.","related":["[[PER-0004-niels-bohr]]","[[PER-0003-albert-einstein]]"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},